507
00:30:17,566 --> 00:30:20,981
Ginny Miller.
His aunt on his mother's side.

508
00:30:21,054 --> 00:30:23,291
You got authorization
from Aunt Ginny?

509
00:30:23,358 --> 00:30:25,267
I gave her a call
