520
00:31:20,642 --> 00:31:24,254
Well, then you got everything.
See you tomorrow, Luther.

521
00:31:24,322 --> 00:31:26,177
Not if see you first.

522
00:31:28,418 --> 00:31:30,328
Now don't forget.
When Sally gets back, you're my witness.

