00:32:14,406 --> 00:32:16,862
Danny, take the 12 years.
It's a gift.

536
00:32:17,895 --> 00:32:19,750
You don't believe their story,
do you?

537
00:32:19,815 --> 00:32:21,887
You think they ought to go to jail
