690
00:42:05,368 --> 00:42:07,278
I tell you I discourage
the practice...

691
00:42:07,353 --> 00:42:09,327
in accordance
with the commander's directive.

692
00:42:09,400 --> 00:42:12,303
Off the record,
I tell you it is an invaluable part...

693
00:42:12,377 --> 00:42:14,231
of close-infantry training.

694
00:42:14,297 --> 00:42:18,071
And if it happens to go on
without my knowledge, so be it.

695
00:42:18,136 --> 00:42:21,039
I run my unit how I run my unit.

696
00:42:21,114 --> 00:42:25,370
You want to investigate me,
roll the dice and take your chances.

697
00:42:25,434 --> 00:42:29,744
I eat breakfast 300 yards from
4,000 Cubans who are trained to kill me.

698
00:42:29,818 --> 00:42:32,785
So don't think for one second that
you can come down here...

699
00:42:32,858 --> 00:42:34,866
flash a badge...

700
00:42:34,939 --> 00:42:37,426
and make me nervous.

701
00:42:41,403 --> 00:42:42,613
Let's go.

702
00:42:45,500 --> 00:42:48,948
Colonel, I'll just need a copy
of Santiago’s transfer order.

703
00:42:49,532 --> 00:42:50,547
What's that?

704
00:42:50,621 --> 00:42:53,620
Santiago's transfer order. You guys
have paperwork on that kind of thing.

705
00:42:53,692 --> 00:42:55,547
I just need it for the file.

706
00:42:55,612 --> 00:42:58,482
- For the file.
- Yeah.

