00:46:22,861 --> 00:46:24,836
Yes, sir. I know you do, sir.

761
00:46:24,910 --> 00:46:26,983
- Fuck you, Harold!
- All right.

762
00:46:27,983 --> 00:46:30,349
At ease.

763
00:46:30,414 --> 00:46:32,270
- Let's sort this thing out.
