765
00:46:35,694 --> 00:46:37,963
Lieutenant Kendrick says
that he gave strict instructions...

766
00:46:38,030 --> 00:46:40,038
that nothing was to happen
to Santiago.

767
00:46:40,111 --> 00:46:43,046
