and hadn't told us...

786
00:47:35,827 --> 00:47:38,478
he'd be violating about 14 articles
of the Code of Ethics.

787
00:47:38,548 --> 00:47:39,923
He has enough to worry about...

788
00:47:39,988 --> 00:47:41,996
God forbid our clients
decide to plead not guilty...

789
00:47:42,069 --> 00:47:44,207
and testify for the record
that they were given an order.

790
00:47:44,276 --> 00:47:46,798
Kendrick specifically told those men
not to touch Santiago.

791
00:47:46,870 --> 00:47:48,658
That's right. And then he went
into Dawson and Downey's room...

792
00:47:48,725 --> 00:47:50,634
and specifically told them
to give him a Code Red.

793
00:47:50,709 --> 00:47:53,327
- Kendrick said different. Have proof?
- He's lying. I have the defendants.

794
00:47:53,397 --> 00:47:55,438
And I have 23 Marines
who aren't accused of murder...

795
00:47:55,510 --> 00:47:57,713
and a lieutenant
with four letters of commendation.

796
00:47:57,781 --> 00:47:59,887
- Why did Markinson go U.A.?
- We'll never know.

797
00:47:59,958 --> 00:48:02,828
- You don't think I could subpoena him?
- You can try, but you won't find him.

798
00:48:02,903 --> 00:48:06,612
You know what he did for the first 17
of his 26 years in the Corps?

799
00:48:06,678 --> 00:48:10,956
Counterintelligence. Markinson's gone.
There is no Markinson.

800
00:48:12,406 --> 00:48:14,261
Look, Danny.

801
00:48:14,326 --> 00:48:16,748
Jessup's star is on the rise.

802
00:48:16,823 --> 00:48:18,679
Division will give me
a lot of room on this one...

803
00:48:18,744 --> 00:48:20,849
to spare Jessup
and the Corps any embarrassment.

804
00:48:20,920 --> 00:48:22,032
How much?

805
00:48:23,160 --> 00:48:26,576
Involuntary manslaughter,
two years, they're home in six months.

806
00:48:26,649 --> 00:48:28,055
No deal. We're going to court.

807
00:48:28,120 --> 00:48:29,875
- No, you're not.
- Why not?

808
00:48:29,943 --> 00:48:33,108
'Cause you’ll lose,
and Danny knows it.

809
00:48:33,176 --> 00:48:35,794
If we do go to court,
I'm gonna have to go all the way.

810
00:48:35,864 --> 00:48:38,101
