whatever punishment they give.

850
00:50:37,411 --> 00:50:40,728
But I believe I was right, sir.
I believe I did my job...

851
00:50:40,804 --> 00:50:44,000
and I will not dishonor myself,
my unit or the Corps...

852
00:50:44,067 --> 00:50:47,963
so that I can go home
in six months...

853
00:50:48,037 --> 00:50:49,411
sir.

854
00:50:56,325 --> 00:51:00,930
Commander, I'd like to talk to Lance
Corporal Dawson alone for a minute.

