00:51:09,094 --> 00:51:11,429
- It's gonna be okay.
- Sit down.

859
00:51:22,406 --> 00:51:24,349
You don't like me very much, do you?

860
00:51:25,608 --> 00:51:28,673
Forget it. Don't answer that.
It doesn't matter.

