00:51:49,801 --> 00:51:52,135
- Do you think we were right?
- It doesn't matter--

866
00:51:52,201 --> 00:51:56,096
- Do you think we were right?
- I think you’d lose.

867
00:51:57,993 --> 00:51:59,849
