868
00:51:59,914 --> 00:52:02,370
I can't believe
they let you wear a uniform.

869
00:52:04,650 --> 00:52:07,170
I'm not gonna feel responsible for this.
I did everything I could.

870
00:52:07,243 --> 00:52:09,664
You're going to Leavenworth
for the better part of your life.

871
00:52:09,739 --> 00:52:11,594
And you know what?
I don't give a shit.

872
00:52:13,579 --> 00:52:16,427
What happened to saluting an officer
when he leaves the room?

873
00:52:25,132 --> 00:52:26,179
Open it up.

874
00:52:28,832 --> 00:52:30,557
I don't believe it.

875
00:52:30,625 --> 00:52:32,926
Dawson's gonna go to jail
just to spite me.

876
00:52:32,992 --> 00:52:35,447
Fine. If he wants to jump
off a cliff, that's his business.

877
00:52:35,520 --> 00:52:39,132
I'm not gonna hold his hand on the way.
I want to get him a new lawyer. How?

878
00:52:39,200 --> 00:52:41,536
Just make a motion tomorrow morning
at the arraignment.

879
00:52:41,602 --> 00:52:43,511
