- I want you to let them be judged.

885
00:52:57,506 --> 00:53:00,290
I want you to stand up
and make an argument.

886
00:53:00,356 --> 00:53:02,909
An argument that didn't work
for Calley at My Lai.

887
00:53:02,980 --> 00:53:05,019
An argument that didn't work
for the Nazis at Nuremburg.

888
00:53:05,091 --> 00:53:06,946
Oh, for Christ's sake, Sam.

889
00:53:07,011 --> 00:53:09,346
